#: pages/images.py:276
msgid "Below you will find all images saved for this tablet. Click the **name** of an image to rename it. The three buttons under each image let you **send it as the suspended image** (:material/cloud_upload:), set it as the **preferred image** (:material/star:) — used as priority during deployment — or **delete** it (:material/delete:). At the bottom of the page you can **retrieve the image currently displayed on the tablet** or **add a new image from your computer** — it will be automatically converted to the correct format and dimensions."
